## Goal
Track reverse dependencies (who imports this file) for true blast radius.

## Implementation
```typescript
// After all files processed
const importedBy = new Map<string, string[]>();

for (const [file, imports] of allImports) {
  for (const imp of imports) {
    const resolved = resolveImportPath(imp, file);
    if (resolved) {
      if (!importedBy.has(resolved)) importedBy.set(resolved, []);
      importedBy.get(resolved).push(file);
    }
  }
}

// Update Qdrant payloads
```

